《'''藏愛'''》<ref>{{Cite web |title=博客來-瑪麗亞凱莉 / 藏愛 (2CD) |url=https://www.books.com.tw/products/0020219088 |website=博客來 |accessdate=2021-01-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123162145/https://www.books.com.tw/products/0020219088 |archivedate=2021-01-23 |language=zh |deadurl=no }}</ref>（{{lang-en|''The Rarities''}}）是美國女歌手[[瑪麗·嘉兒|瑪麗·嘉兒]]的第八張[[合輯|合輯]]，將於2020年10月2日由[[哥倫比亞唱片公司|哥倫比亞唱片公司]]及{{le|Legacy唱片|Legacy Records}}發行。此專輯為瑪麗·嘉兒出道三十週年企劃「MC30」的一部份，與嘉兒的[[自傳|自傳]]《{{le|The Meaning of Mariah Carey}}》於相若時間發行。專輯包含從未發佈、具有嘉兒個人意義的作品。CD2則為嘉兒1996年於日本[[東京巨蛋|東京巨蛋]]舉行的《[[夢遊仙境_(瑪麗亞·凱莉專輯)#夢遊仙境世界巡迴演唱會|夢遊仙境巡回演唱會]]》的[[現場專輯|現場專輯]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Ashwad |first=Jem |title=Mariah Carey to Release ''Rarities'' Album |url=https://variety.com/2020/music/news/mariah-carey-rarities-album-1234739917/ |website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |accessdate=August 19, 2020 |date=August 19, 2020 |archive-date=2020-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200901124643/https://variety.com/2020/music/news/mariah-carey-rarities-album-1234739917/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Lovece |first=Frank |title=LI's Mariah Carey to release new album in October |url=https://www.newsday.com/entertainment/music/mariah-carey-album-the-rarities-1.48291319 |website=Newsday |accessdate=August 19, 2020 |date=August 19, 2020 |archive-date=2020-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821015107/https://www.newsday.com/entertainment/music/mariah-carey-album-the-rarities-1.48291319 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=Mariah Carey Handpicks Favorites From Her Vault for ''The Rarities'' Album, Coming Friday, October 2 |url=https://www.legacyrecordings.com/2020/08/19/mariah-carey-handpicks-favorites-from-her-vault-for-the-rarities-album-coming-friday-october-2/ |publisher=Legacy Records |accessdate=August 19, 2020 |date=August 19, 2020 |archive-date=2020-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903152805/https://legacyrecordings.com/2020/08/19/mariah-carey-handpicks-favorites-from-her-vault-for-the-rarities-album-coming-friday-october-2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。日本區專輯更附送當年演唱會的[[藍光影碟|藍光影碟]]<ref>{{cite press release |title=【デビュー30周年記念】世界的歌姫の軌跡を辿る“裏ベスト”アルバム『レアリティーズ』10月発売！日本盤のみ1996年東京ドーム初来日公演ライヴ映像を特別収録した豪華３枚組！ |trans-title=[30th Anniversary of Debut] "Back Best" album "Rarities", which traces the trajectory of the world diva, will be released in October! Only the Japanese edition, a luxurious three-disc set that specially recorded the live image of Tokyo Dome's first performance in Japan in 1996! |url=https://www.sonymusic.co.jp/artist/MariahCarey/info/521228 |publisher=Sony Music Entertainment Japan |language=ja |accessdate=August 19, 2020 |date=August 19, 2020 |archive-date=2020-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200910155320/https://www.sonymusic.co.jp/artist/MariahCarey/info/521228 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 宣傳及發行 ==
2020年8月19日，瑪麗嘉兒於社交平台宣佈正式預售《藏愛》，發售日期為2020年10月2日。同日，她於《[[早安美國|早安美國]]》節目中演唱出道單曲〈[[愛的幻影|愛的幻影]]〉及歌曲〈{{le|Close My Eyes|Close My Eyes (Mariah Carey song)}}〉<ref name=gma>{{cite news |url=https://www.goodmorningamerica.com/culture/story/mariah-carey-shares-details-upcoming-album-fans-72466528 |title=Mariah Carey shares details about her upcoming album: 'This one is for you, my fans' |publisher=Good Morning America |last=FitzPatrick |first=Hayley |date=August 19, 2020 |accessdate=August 19, 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820103051/https://www.goodmorningamerica.com/culture/story/mariah-carey-shares-details-upcoming-album-fans-72466528 |archivedate=2020-08-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月9日，嘉兒公開曲目單。

==專業評價==
《[[公告牌_(雜誌)|公告牌]]》把《藏愛》列為「2020秋季等不及要聽的專輯」<ref>{{cite web |author1=Jason Lipshutz |author2=Keith Caulfield |title=Fall Music Preview 2020: The Albums We Can’t Wait to Hear (and the Ones We Hope Finally Arrive) |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/podcasts/9445911/fall-music-preview-2020-pop-shop-podcast |website=Billboard |accessdate=2020-09-09 |date=2020-09-08 |archive-date=2020-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200909015525/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/podcasts/9445911/fall-music-preview-2020-pop-shop-podcast |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

